{"tid":1588394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解假得咁明顯 對家都仲要講大話？","createTime":"2019-09-22T20:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T22:59:16.000Z","uid":180349,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a410313e8e691654dd150d56b276da41fde8d4ab","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:04:04.000Z","msg":"抗爭持續左過百日，中間發生左好多事，大家都有目共睹。係八月五號，政府宣布開始每日狗記者會，有睇過狗記者會既人就知佢地講既野好on9好荒謬，但時至今日，佢地一直都講緊啲荒謬既大話。<br />\n<br />\n例子多到數唔到，例如話冇收到爆眼少女既去信，七二一唔見白衫人有武器，警察使用最低武力，過期tg冇害，佢地識分辦市民同示威者但電光火石間會分唔到示威者同記者等等。 同時亦會用過分既言語偽術去誤導同掩飾佢地做既事，例如用腳推開市民，警察係專業克制，海棉彈等等。唔單只係狗會，仲有cctvb同各大藍報社都係咁。好多謊言明眼人一眼睇穿，但點解佢地仍然咁做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢地既目標唔係你地，主要係一班對時事冇乜主動性，一味被動接收資訊既人，呢類人其實都佔好大部分，簡單啲講佢地係人稱既&rdquo;港豬&rdquo;。因為呢件事對佢地影響唔大，唔會主動去接收資訊，又習慣性地睇cctvb，透過單一既渠道獲訊息，部分既人仲會因為覺得cctvb新聞同狗會係一種好official 既媒體，相信佢地講既野，慢慢被潛移默化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者大家覺得呢班人爭唔過，但佢地真係佔數唔少，係大家重視既民意都佔一部分。多左呢部分民意，手足做野就有更高正當性。多左呢部分民意，班垃圾藍絲廢老就唔敢亂搞事。多左呢部分民意，日後既重要選舉我地可以有更多揸拿。<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多，我都係想大家正視下呢個問題，因為每次見到有cctvb新聞或者狗記者會，身邊既人可能得啖笑就冇左回事，甚至對佢地即謊言開始麻木冇感覺。我都會覺得好灰，因為每播多一鐘，就有人被洗腦多一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n對於呢個問題，我有些少建議(個人睇法，未必最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n-對於一啲識用腦諗野既港豬，有好多人一嚟就屌佢地港豬，但其實冇乜用，佢地只會覺得煩更加唔想去接觸相關既野。與其怪責佢地，不如試下主動提供更多更全面既資訊，又可以提出證據反對家即謊言，等佢地明辯是非。或者多啲講下事件對佢地既影響，提高返佢地對呢個運動既積極性。<br />\n<br />\n-而對於一啲讀書少又冇腦冇批判思考既人，佢地唔少因爲咁俾人洗藍，我地先唔好鬧佢地，我認為可以試下代入下藍絲陣營，用返佢地擅長既誇張煽情方式洗返佢地腦，對家誇張，我地更誇張，對家煽情，我地更煽情，成功的話就多一個人企我地呢邊。唔需要注重fact check，因為佢地根本冇腦分真假。記住要有耐性，對家做緊既就係「謊言重複一千次便是真理」，我地都可以做到，長輩圖係一個好好既參考例子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-仲有一啲人係眼中只有利益，立場都只係隨利益擺動既人，聲稱自己中立，消費呢場抗爭既人。我冇咩建議，我勸大家都係唔好曬心機，除左利益冇野可以改變佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外當然仲有其他巴絲既建議:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-扺制tvb，罷買tvb廣告商<br />\n-係連儂牆做返罷睇cctvb 狗記者會既 教佢地轉台睇rthk <br />\n-發完夢當日和理非手足要多啲文宣助攻<br />\n-睇多啲資訊，唔洗到突發狀況口啞啞<br />\n-我腦容量有限，希望大家集思廣益，提多啲建議<br />\n<br />\n仲有當然就係將呢啲訊息spread開去啦，<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係咁多，如果講漏講錯，唔該糾正我。<br />\n第一次開po可能有甩漏，請大家多多包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n我相信香港人會贏"},{"pid":"730e7583ff6ae79f87d275fed17277e5ccdbd80b","tid":1588394,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"f3a5437203bc2692e6e36cb8685165b39cb1256f","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"訓唔着 用左兩個鐘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望會有人睇下"},{"pid":"70e0844a9233982f8965f390097047accd041ec1","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:11:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8366aef40587ebf0d61cf65bdde8d3cdd24df140","tid":1588394,"uid":128516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3a5437203bc2692e6e36cb8685165b39cb1256f","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"訓唔着 用左兩個鐘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望會有人睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:13:54.000Z","msg":"散播恐慌<br />\n話比你聽我地係講大話你都耐我地唔可"},{"pid":"5646ba5a9b304a98632f89f30e35e2cf0fe6234c","tid":1588394,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:14:21.000Z","msg":"其實就所有嘢都有進行緊，唔係邊得嚟咁多師奶支持，只係有啲繼續裝睡，有啲真無腦。<br />\n<br />\n而對面講大話，係因為唔敢面對事實，佢哋嘅自尊心唔容許人挑戰，佢哋明知自己錯，但佢哋驚認錯，因為有嚴重嘅後果，人越驚就越要圍爐，所以你會見到上面俾緊信心佢哋。但圍爐圍得太埋，就會引火自焚，到時大家只需要睇住佢死，踩多兩腳就得，無需可憐。"},{"pid":"f9ad797dd9d636cf97d79913e405025965c5e9e9","tid":1588394,"uid":26467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:18:38.000Z","msg":"因為佢既對象唔係了解件事既人"},{"pid":"937872efec06c6398703edce073ea2410d43bf68","tid":1588394,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:20:59.000Z","msg":"分化"},{"pid":"a179933e8734ba123aabccd9a9a05fb718372525","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5646ba5a9b304a98632f89f30e35e2cf0fe6234c","tid":1588394,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:14:21.000Z","msg":"其實就所有嘢都有進行緊，唔係邊得嚟咁多師奶支持，只係有啲繼續裝睡，有啲真無腦。<br />\n<br />\n而對面講大話，係因為唔敢面對事實，佢哋嘅自尊心唔容許人挑戰，佢哋明知自己錯，但佢哋驚認錯，因為有嚴重嘅後果，人越驚就越要圍爐，所以你會見到上面俾緊信心佢哋。但圍爐圍得太埋，就會引火自焚，到時大家只需要睇住佢死，踩多兩腳就得，無需可憐。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:21:26.000Z","msg":"我女朋友呀媽係藍，我用長輩圖攻勢洗到佢懷疑人生，雖然最後冇將佢洗黄，但佢由好支持黑警俾我洗到好驚黑警，聽到警察唔敢出街，嚟緊我會繼續努力洗下佢"},{"pid":"49268f5f126c52b971837292bf65caf20225d169","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8366aef40587ebf0d61cf65bdde8d3cdd24df140","tid":1588394,"uid":128516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3a5437203bc2692e6e36cb8685165b39cb1256f","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"訓唔着 用左兩個鐘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望會有人睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:13:54.000Z","msg":"散播恐慌<br />\n話比你聽我地係講大話你都耐我地唔可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:24:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲我諗係鄉黑思維"},{"pid":"6a0aff0e430b6adaa0c81b5408cb9ae2f2fc1f68","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"937872efec06c6398703edce073ea2410d43bf68","tid":1588394,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:20:59.000Z","msg":"分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:27:12.000Z","msg":"啱 呢招都幾大傷害 但暫時唔係好覺係對家陣容出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />似係對家分化我地多"},{"pid":"e19fd7c764a259075f789048f0e5a6ef8922c213","tid":1588394,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a5437203bc2692e6e36cb8685165b39cb1256f","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"訓唔着 用左兩個鐘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望會有人睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:29:18.000Z","msg":"有啦 原來真係咁多人瞓唔著"},{"pid":"836877fa20f81b80988824ed8b3231b7ee0b33e1","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e19fd7c764a259075f789048f0e5a6ef8922c213","tid":1588394,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a5437203bc2692e6e36cb8685165b39cb1256f","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"訓唔着 用左兩個鐘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望會有人睇下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:29:18.000Z","msg":"有啦 原來真係咁多人瞓唔著"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:39:16.000Z","msg":"唉 講真 呢三個月好多晚都訓得唔好"},{"pid":"79747009be7835e735e784cce9be04c34258a064","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:53:32.000Z","msg":"睇住對家既抹黑，荒謬得好撚緊要<br />\n有撚埋價錢表，死既又坳返生，又老屈<br />\n但都係有一定既影響力<br />\n文宣都係一個戰線 唔能夠輕敵<br />\n我地既對手唔只係班藍絲<br />\n仲有班黑警 黑社會 港共政府 中共政府<br />\n佢地出盡計打壓我地 分化我地 抹黑我地<br />\n如果淨係睇連登ig連儂牆 就覺得我地文宣做足<br />\n咁就錯曬<br />\n我地既戰線可以擴展到紙幣 黨鐵車廂 或者更多地方(其他po見到)"},{"pid":"30e4371c0ec0c23703ff70bc8bf3463c527d5e95","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"719554f23257fa66530856d8da856e49d379fa86","tid":1588394,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebfaf585a3092e5e740bd20280c8aa6b513d9f0","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"死黑警不得好死"},{"pid":"6845020cd5aa9eff98faa32806b44832a1c6f0ec","tid":1588394,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾獎得主索忍尼辛的一段話：<br />\n「我們知道他們在說謊，他們也知道自己是說謊，他們也知道我們知道他們在說謊，我們也知道他們知道我們知道他們說謊，但是他們依然在說謊」。"},{"pid":"8cbf9829455d720361a2e51227d5002e2006f0c5","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"［有圖］［經濟制裁TVB] 廣告商名單整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253538</a>"},{"pid":"f71c555354e7975b29975f89a0f3c029a4f6f5f4","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6845020cd5aa9eff98faa32806b44832a1c6f0ec","tid":1588394,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾獎得主索忍尼辛的一段話：<br />\n「我們知道他們在說謊，他們也知道自己是說謊，他們也知道我們知道他們在說謊，我們也知道他們知道我們知道他們說謊，但是他們依然在說謊」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:26:07.000Z","msg":"呢句我repost左好多次 每次提起都好灰"},{"pid":"e08a83c8d3931a284d747512105d4121fc99cb1d","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"深黃老母尋晚睇新聞突然問 : 今次運動係咪變咗質？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588540</a><br />\n<br />\n我老閪都話對面郁手先 而事實都係<br />\n不過個921玻璃樽廢中俾對家擇左嚟做核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e3d482778715d6cc00073bed6ff6d0014b3b97","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"92b45fc5a1cb6fedb11788807b84a5668d8f8bd2","tid":1588394,"uid":180349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"仲有要增加返民間記者會既覆蓋範圍，ig得5.8萬人咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi